\": 282, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"the most-visited country\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 340}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"a year-round hit\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Add in the biggest multi-sport show on earth and you can see how the city will also be one of the world's busiest cities this summer.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest multi-sport show\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"earth\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's busiest cities\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cThe hotel industry is looking to welcome all those visitors for the Olympics and Paralympics.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hotel industry\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"all those visitors\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet according to the hospitality sector, there are still issues surrounding staff working during the 2024 Games that have not been ironed out with the city and Games authorities.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hospitality sector\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"staff\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Games\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"the city and Games authorities\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Will we be able to find enough staff to welcome the tourists who will be coming to Paris?\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0686393766483124e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enough staff\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"the tourists\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is also the question of training new employees,\\\" said David Zenouda, president for the Paris region of the Union of Trade and Hospitality Industries.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0686393766483124e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"new employees\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"David Zenouda\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"the Union\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"Trade and Hospitality Industries\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris will be a busy city this summer.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0686393766483124e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a busy city\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/Michel Euler/CFP \\\"We are starting to get some answers about delivery and logistics.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1112, \"end\": 