.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The mayor\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is urging them to stay to enjoy the Olympic and Paralympic atmosphere.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic atmosphere\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hundreds of thousands of people traditionally leave the city in the summer and go on holiday.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hundreds of thousands\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1667}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"holiday\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the mayor's plea, many locals say they are still planning to head out - and try to make some money while they are away.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mayor's plea\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"many locals\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"some money\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The local government is doubling subway fares and tripling the tourist tax during the Games.\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The local government\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"subway fares\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1903}, {\"ngram\": \"the tourist tax\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1932}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For the Olympics and Paralympics, the Paris capital region transport body will increase its transport options considerably,\\\" said Valerie Pecresse, president of the Paris capital region.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1991, \"end\": 1996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0686393766483124e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2083, \"end\": 2090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Little_Red_Riding_Hood\", \"score\": 0.7179285123412824, \"rank\": 0.3928963287381289, \"text\": \"Valerie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Little_Red_Riding_Hood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Little_Red_Riding_Hood\"}, {\"begin\": 2118, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0686393766483124e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"its transport options\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is unthinkable that locals would pay for this.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we are going to create a new transport pass to allow people to move around the whole Paris capital region.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2280, \"end\": 2285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0686393766483124e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new transport pass\", \"from\": 2218, \